<div class="exercise">
<div class="exercise-header">
<div><span class="exercise-id">Exercise L22-2</span> <span class="exercise-lecture">(Lecture 22)</span></div>
<div class="exercise-tags"><a class="tag" href="../study_outline.md#module-8-power-series-taylor-series-applications" target="_blank">taylor-series</a> <a class="tag" href="../study_outline.md#module-8-power-series-taylor-series-applications" target="_blank">high-order-derivatives</a> <a class="tag" href="../study_outline.md#module-8-power-series-taylor-series-applications" target="_blank">maclaurin-series</a></div>
</div>
